{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"12aaaf88f4","title":"毛泽东关于转发广东省委关于贯彻郑州会议精神的报告的批语","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"666c1f4ecc","index":0,"year":1959,"month":3,"day":13,"articleId":"12aaaf88f4"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"33e96eaa69","type":"title","text":"毛泽东关于转发广东省委关于贯彻郑州会议精神的报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"12aaaf88f4"},{"id":"91efe21412","type":"appellation","text":"小平同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"12aaaf88f4"},{"id":"8b46d324c8","type":"paragraph","text":"广东省委三月十一日报告很好，请你用电话方式，于今日立即转发各省、市、区党委，供参考。广东行动迅速，一面开会，一面即将方针直达各生产队长，毫不拖泥带水。湖北的方针三月八日即下达各生产队，广东于三月十二日下达，也是很快的。各地宜仿此，一面开会，一面迅即下达方针。广东的“三定五放”，符合郑州会议精神，请各地研究，酌情采纳。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"12aaaf88f4"},{"id":"7f5e7ce93a","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东1959年3月13日上午五时，于武昌","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"12aaaf88f4"}],"page":{"id":"5cde866ee0","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"12aaaf88f4","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}